Label
Training Dataset
Testing Dataset
Prediction
Model
Algorithm

Understood how each component contributes to building an effective Machine Learning model.

Classification vs Regression

Received a detailed explanation of the two major types of supervised learning.

Classification

Learned that classification algorithms predict categorical outputs.

Examples:

Spam or Not Spam
Pass or Fail
Disease Present or Not Present
Genuine or Fake Product
Positive or Negative Sentiment

Common classification algorithms discussed:

Logistic Regression
Decision Tree Classifier
K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN)
Support Vector Machine (SVM)
Random Forest Classifier
Regression

Learned that regression algorithms predict continuous numerical values.

Examples:

House Price Prediction
Salary Prediction
Temperature Forecasting
Sales Prediction
Stock Price Estimation

Common regression algorithms discussed:

Linear Regression
Decision Tree Regressor
Random Forest Regressor

Compared regression and classification problems with practical examples to understand their differences.

